g.title: Rhombicuboctahedron
g.desc: Leonardo da Vinci’s drawing of a rhombicuboctahedron, as published in Pacioli’s De divina proportione. See https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/De_divina_proportione about the book, and https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rhombicuboctahedron about the geometric solid. Curiously, the word rhombicuboctahedron does not appear in dictionary.com. :-0
